Here’s an in detail video of how #MukuchyanArtistry created the beautiful rainy day looks for the @samantchauhan show! 

This is one of my favourite looks created by #MukuchyanArtistry for @fdciofficial X @lakmefashionwk

Still feels like a dream in so many ways to see the result of my passion project coming to life ♥️ 

I teamed up with Eucerin to help them develop an already best seller product into a tinted version and now 3 years later, I am standing on the stage in South America and speaking and educating about this product with my face on such giant posters advertising it! 🥰

I’m still processing the success and love I took home with me 🙈

@eucerin.mx and all the people who made this event such a stellar one… you have my heart ♥️🙏🏼

Eucerin x Marianna Mukuchyan

I’ve visited the Mexico City a few times in the past, but this time round it was just so special, it was for the launch of my hardwork and passion; the new and advanced Eucerin, sun oil control tinted! 

For the first time a dermatological brand and a makeup artist, experts from the field of beauty and science teamed up to develop this advanced technology sunscreen with so many more benefits than just UVA and UVB protection! ☀️

I’m so grateful for this wonderful opportunity with such an international brand like @eucerin.mx and I look forward to all the future collaborations with the team ♥️
